OL,3,CWelsh Water to cut up to 500 jobs over
OL,4,Cthe next two years
OL,6,FDwr Cymru Welsh Water says it will cut
OL,7,Fup to 500 staff as part of a
OL,8,Frestructuring of its business.
OL,10,FThe move would see a reduction of its
OL,11,Fworkforce by 12%, which the company
OL,12,Fsays will allow it to "protect and
OL,13,Fenhance frontline services."
OL,15,FIt says the cuts will be achieved by
OL,16,F"redesigning processes and ways of
OL,17,Fworking" along with increasing
OL,18,Fefficiencies across the business.
