OL,3,CWelsh Water to cut up to 500 jobs over
OL,4,Cthe next two years
OL,6,FWelsh Water cited "significant
OL,7,Fpressures of the water sector" and the
OL,8,Fneed for greater investment in
OL,9,Finfrastructure.
OL,11,FIn 2025-26, average customer bills
OL,12,Fhave risen by 27%, following the
OL,13,Fagreement of the latest investment
OL,14,Fperiod with regulator Ofwat.
OL,16,FThe company says it will invest more
OL,17,Fthan #4bn in its services over the
OL,18,Fnext five years.
