OL,3,CWelsh Water to cut up to 500 jobs over
OL,4,Cthe next two years
OL,6,FPete Perry, Chief Executive of Welsh
OL,7,FWater, said: "Our customers'
OL,8,Fexpectations have changed
OL,9,Fsignificantly in recent years, as have
OL,10,Four regulatory requirements, and as a
OL,11,Fcompany we need to adapt.
OL,13,F"With customers' bills increasing, we
OL,14,Fhave challenged ourselves hard to
OL,15,Freduce our own costs to ensure every
OL,16,Fpound we spend brings benefit to
OL,17,Fcustomers and maintains our financial
OL,18,Fresilience during a challenging period
OL,19,Ffor the sector."
